import { Button, Card, Col, Container, Form, Row} from 'react-bootstrap';
import React from 'react';

function ProfileDetails() {
  
  return (
    <Form className="m-4 w-">
      <Form.Group as={Row}  controlId="formProfileDetailsName" >
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">FirstName</Form.Label>
        <Col sm="6">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Enter First Name" />
        </Col>
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">LastName</Form.Label>
        <Col sm="6">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Enter Last Name" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formProfileDetailsTitle" >
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">Title</Form.Label>
        <Col sm="12">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Enter Title" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formProfileDetailsLocation" >
        <Form.Label column className="sr-only">Location</Form.Label>
        <Col sm="12">
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder="Enter Your Location" />
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
      <Button type="submit">Save</Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default ProfileDetails;
